overview: Starrcade 2019 takes place on Sunday, Dec. 1 from Infinite Energy Arena in Duluth, Georgia. The event will begin inside the arena at 6:30 p.m. ET with one hour airing on WWE Network. In the main event, "The Fiend" Bray Wyatt will defend the WWE universal championship in the cage against Braun Strowman. Other big matches include rivalries such as Roman Reigns vs. Baron Corbin and New Day vs. The Revival.
title: WWE Starrcade
